name: CustomerAgreement
description: Defines the customer-related terms, including service level agreements, privacy terms, and user responsibilities.

name: CustomerPolicy
description: Policy for managing customer data, outlining data retention, processing, and privacy regulations.

name: ProductLicense
description: Covers licensing details for products, including terms of use, product rights, and restrictions.

name: ConsumerDataProcessingAgreement
description: Agreement governing the processing of consumer data, ensuring compliance with GDPR and other privacy laws.

name: FinancialTransactionTerms
description: Outlines terms related to financial transactions, including transaction fees, refunds, and payment terms.
